# Build outputs — never commit. This crate is workspace-excluded and builds
# into its own target/, which must stay out of version control.
/target/

# Cargo package dry-run output (.crate tarballs, extracted verify dirs).
**/*.crate

# Toolchain / compiler scratch artifacts.
.rustc_info.json
**/*.rlib
**/*.rmeta
**/*.rs.bk

# zkVM guest / proof outputs (would only exist under an authorized toolchain,
# which is ABSENT here): guest ELF/image binaries, receipts/proofs, image-id
# caches, and any guest scaffolding directory.
**/*.elf
**/*.bin
**/riscv-guest/
**/*.receipt
**/*.proof

# Run logs / scratch output.
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
